  "response": "The Indian Statistical Institute (ISI) admits students based on their performance in the entrance exam and interview for its various programs. For the Bachelor of Statistics (BSTAT) program at ISI, approximately 50 students are selected each year. However, this number may vary slightly from year to year based on various factors. It is always best to check the latest admission brochure or official ISI website for the most accurate and updated information.",
